Probability Layer
│
├── 1. Input Logits
│     ├── Output from LM Head
│     └── Shape: (batch_size × seq_len × vocab_size)
│
├── 2. Logit Processing (optional)
│     │
│     ├── Temperature Scaling
│     │      └── logits / temperature
│     │
│     ├── Logit Bias Adjustment
│     │      └── add bias to specific tokens
│     │
│     └── Logit Clipping (optional)
│
├── 3. Numerical Stabilization
│     │
│     ├── Maximum Logit Extraction
│     │      └── max(logits)
│     │
│     └── Logit Shift
│            └── logits − max(logits)
│
├── 4. Exponentiation
│     └── exp(logits)
│
├── 5. Normalization Constant
│     └── Sum of exponentials
│
├── 6. Softmax Probability Computation
│     └── exp(logit_i) / Σ exp(logits)
│
├── 7. Probability Tensor
│     ├── Shape: (batch_size × seq_len × vocab_size)
│     └── Values between 0 and 1
│
├── 8. Optional Log Probability Conversion
│     └── log_softmax
│
└── 9. Output Distribution
      └── Passed to decoding / sampling module